  {
    "key": "6e32b3066dc7c0e944877c0ded3b5eefb31f0813877d15cd1dd70d1bdd8b7c1e",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_05.png[/img] With rations down to nothing, %ratcatcher% feebly enters your tent, the moans of some hungry men passing by before the flaps close behind him. He explains that he has a resolution to your food problem. You fear to ask what it is, but you've little choice now. The ratchatcher swings a burlap sack onto the table. Some shape of it moves, skittering and bobbing and squealing. The man smashes it with his fist before smiling at you.%SPEECH_ON%Sorry, had a live one there!%SPEECH_OFF%He explains that rat isn't the most nutritious of animals, nor the healthiest, but it'd help the company enough until they can get back to a town or farm. You reluctantly agree to keep your men from starving.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_05.png[/img] With rations down to nothing, %ratcatcher% feebly enters your tent, the moans of some hungry men passing by before the flaps close behind him. He explains that he has a resolution to your food problem. You fear to ask what it is, but you've little choice now. The ratchatcher swings a burlap sack onto the table. Some shape of it moves, skittering and bobbing and squealing. The man smashes it with his fist before smiling at you.%SPEECH_ON%Sorry, had a live one there!%SPEECH_OFF%He explains that rat isn't the most nutritious of animals, nor the healthiest, but it'd help the company enough until they can get back to a town or farm. You reluctantly agree to keep your men from starving.\""
  },
